K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503a-1: bo dhi garbh'a lang+k'a ra laksha dh'a ra ni /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503a-3: byang chub kyi snying po'i rgyan 'bum gyi gzungs /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //

K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-1: pra bh'a sa ke tu m'urdha ne /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-4: na mo bha ga ba te sh'akya mu na ye /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-9: bo dha ni bo dha ni /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-10: sarba ta th'a ga ta go tsa re /

K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-17: sarba ta th'a ga t'a bhi shi ka te /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-18: gu ne gu na ba te /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-19: sarba buddh'a shu n'a ba bh'a se /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-23: sarba ta th'a ga ta aa dhi shthi te /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-26: pra sha me pra sha me /

K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-33: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta bya ba lo ki te /

K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-46: rigs kyi bu mo gang la la zhig gzungs 'di bris te mchod rten byas la /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-47: mchod rten de'i nang du gzungs 'di bcug na des
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-48: mchod rten gcig byas na 'bum byas bar 'gyur ro
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:503b-49: // lha rdzas kyi me tog dang /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-1: ba dan la sogs pas kyang mchod par 'gyur te /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-2: mchod rten 'ba' zhig mchod pa ma yin gyi /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-5: dge 'dun dkon mchog rnams la yang mchod pa'i yo byad de dag gis mchod par 'gyur ro //
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-7: ngas mdo 'di bshad pa ni bsod nams zhan pa dang /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-11: mtshams med pa byed pa dang /
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-16: mtshams med par 'gro ba'i sems can de lta bu dag gi phyir gzungs 'di bshad do //
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-18: phyi ma'i dus phyi ma'i tshe khyim na gnas pa dang /

K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-20: mchod par mi byed pa rnams ji ltar khyim pa
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-21: rnams sdug bsngal bar bshad pa de bzhin du rab
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-22: tu byung ba rnams kyang sdug bsngal bar 'gyur ro
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-23: // de ste de bzhin du sangs rgyas mchod cing
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-24: 'di la nyan pas mchod rten gcig byas na chos
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-25: kyis brgyan pa brgyad khri bzhi stong rnams kyang mchod
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504a-27: bsod nams kyi phung po dpag tu med par 'gyur ro //
K12D0509=D0920_H0478:504b-0: sdong pos brgyan pa bklags shing kha ton du @504b byas par 'gyur ro //
